|{{Dts|1986|December|2}}
|[[Сиэтл Суперсоникс]] (г)
|align=center|В 115—109 (ОТ)<ref>{{cite web
 |url         = http://www.basketball-reference.com/boxscores/198612020SEA.html
 |title       = Chicago Bulls at Seattle Supersonics Box Score, December 2, 1986
